To create an npc look at the following list, a list of functions which is
meant as a checklist. You should call each function with desired values at
creation. To avoid confusion you better use the same order. 

For further information, check manual pages.

 set_name
 set_race
 set_long
 set_gender
 add_adj
 add_lwvs

 set_tmp_stat
   (please initialize all stats somehow)
 set_pot_stat

 set_skill_rank 
 cb_set_parry_skill
 set_move_msg
 set_run_msg

 set_base_hp
 set_hp 
   (after setting base hp)

 set_skill_rank SK_MANA_DEVELOP	
 set_mana 
   (after setting SK_MANA_DEVELOP)

 add_prop LIVE_NPC_MAX_FATIGUE
 set_fatigue 
   (after setting LIVE_NPC_MAX_FATIGUE)

 add_tool_slot
 set_connections

Also you need to define the following functions:
 query_attack_data
 query_hitloc_data
